  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-ON-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package intentionally omits hasApplicabilityConstraint and hasOperatingEnvelope from the ContextOfUse, triggering W-ON-02 (unbounded applicability). All 13 credibility factors are assessed; the package is accepted to surface the ontological gap.",
