      "acceptanceCriteria": "Configuration management and version control documented for all solver components; independent code review completed.",
      "rationale": "Version control is in place and solver release notes are archived, but independent third-party code review has not been completed. Achieved level 3 falls short of required level 4 for MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests and method-of-manufactured-solutions (MMS) verification completed for all governing equations.",
      "rationale": "MMS verification was performed for the Navier-Stokes solver but not for the hemolysis transport sub-model. Achieved level 3 is insufficient for MRL 5."
