      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) reported for hemolysis index QOI across at least three systematically refined meshes.",
      "rationale": "GCI was computed on three mesh levels; however, asymptotic convergence was not fully achieved for the near-impeller boundary layer region. Achieved level 3."
