      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation dataset includes at least 10 independent experimental replicates per operating point with inter-lab reproducibility demonstrated.",
      "rationale": "Only 3 replicates per operating point available; single laboratory. Inter-lab reproducibility not established. Achieved level 2."
    },
